

{"id":6055,"date":"2024-03-04T20:34:48","date_gmt":"2024-03-04T13:34:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/?p=6055"},"modified":"2024-03-11T17:19:43","modified_gmt":"2024-03-11T10:19:43","slug":"6-loi-ich-cua-viec-tap-yoga-vao-buoi-sang","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/6-loi-ich-cua-viec-tap-yoga-vao-buoi-sang\/","title":{"rendered":"6 l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp Yoga v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00e0y m\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n kh\u00f4ng? Bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp Yoga bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap tinh th\u1ea7n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n k\u00edch th\u00edch c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. Trong bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng, c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u0103ng c\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp yoga c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m n\u00f3ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp, t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 linh ho\u1ea1t, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u1edbi. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Yoga gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 lo l\u1eafng, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp Yoga bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 vi\u1ec7c th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u1edf tr\u00ean gi\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c d\u00e0nh 15 ph\u00fat s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp Yoga mang l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ee3i \u00edch b\u1ed5 sung, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng ng\u00e0y m\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng c\u01a1<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi ng\u1ee7, c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u00edch t\u1ee5 c\u00e1c m\u00f4 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u1ecfng khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng. T\u1eadp Yoga gi\u00fap k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t c\u00e1c kh\u1edbp v\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u1ec1m c\u00e1c c\u01a1, gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee9ng kh\u1edbp v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Theo th\u1eddi gian, t\u1eadp Yoga s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u0103ng t\u00ednh linh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 \u0111au nh\u1ee9c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 lo l\u1eafng<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp Yoga x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 lo l\u1eafng. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u0169 b\u1ecf m\u1ecdi c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00e0y m\u1edbi v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng hormone h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yoga t\u1ea1o ra endorphin, serotonin, oxytocin v\u00e0 dopamine, nh\u1eefng hormone l\u00e0m t\u0103ng t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 t\u00e2m tr\u00ed<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. Yoga khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 t\u00e2m tr\u00ed th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp th\u1edf, thi\u1ec1n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tham gia c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u01a1 kh\u00e1c nhau trong m\u1ed7i t\u01b0 th\u1ebf. T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n Yoga gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ki\u1ec3m tra c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 xem n\u00f3 c\u1ea7n g\u00ec trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ec7 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n Yoga bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap k\u00edch th\u00edch h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ti\u00eau h\u00f3a v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh trao \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5t, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch linh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>T\u1ea1o th\u00f3i quen t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00e0y m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u1eadp Yoga c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o ra th\u00f3i quen t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y. Th\u00f3i quen n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 t\u00e2m h\u1ed3n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The New Gym &#8211; Gym cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Email: cskh@thenewgym.vn<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Hotline: 1900 63 69 20<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Facebook: The New Gym<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; Zalo OA: <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/zalo.me\/thenewgym\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https:\/\/zalo.me\/thenewgym<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp: <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/phong-gym-gan-day-the-new-gym-gan-day\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https:\/\/thenew